data.title: Photo agency since 1938
data.meta_description: Portraits of personalities, major events, international politics, fashion, culture, fine arts and historical images from around the world ... Roger-Viollet is 150 years of photography and more than 2 million works from the collections of the City of Paris, the archives of the daily newspaper France-Soir, foreign collections and renowned photographers.
